{"tid":2435485,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦店店員用筆電陳列品瘋狂挖礦 辯稱測試穩定度被炒魷","createTime":"2021-03-06T09:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T06:46:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9aca1f5c8829250e596f28bd64cbb81336d6daf8","tid":2435485,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893841/sme_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893841%2Fsme_1024.jpg&h=63013143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前不少加密貨幣，例如比特幣（Bitcoin ）、以太幣（Ether）價格飈升，引來不少關注。日前台灣高雄一名網民電腦商場時發現，展示出來的筆記型電腦每台都很熱，風扇都在狂轉，再仔細一看，原來筆電都在挖礦。 <br />\n<br />\n前一名台灣網民在 Facebook 群組發帖，指自己到高雄建國路某間店舖看筆記型電腦，發現每部都很熱，細看之下，指其中一部電競筆電在挖礦：「我偷瞄算力都超過 30MH，現場目測大概 5-10 台在跑」。<br />\n<br />\n之後店員顯得有點慌張，辯稱在測試電腦的穩定性。樓主則覺得這樣做有問題，因為可能有消費者買陳列品或特價貨品，但這些商品有可能曾用來挖礦。隨後店員私訊給樓主道歉，說挖礦是他個人行為，店家不知情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893841/del_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893841%2Fdel_1024_600.jpg&h=90f52072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後店方得知事件，指該名員工為獲取個人利益屬不當行為，公司已檢查所有陳列品電腦，並增設防火牆封鎖礦池網址，曾用作挖礦的電腦會另行處理，不會作特價品發售。該名曾用電腦挖礦的員工，則已被免職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2893841/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2893841%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n8lSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=e7f27cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2893841/</a>"},{"pid":"d831eb3265b486c437d50031d33fcd3414ed191e","tid":2435485,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac